{"tid":2174272,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【皇馬傳奇】費高 Twitter 賀美斯離隊：「歷史時刻！！！」","createTime":"2020-08-25T20:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T09:31:41.000Z","uid":165817,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"69fab256819499ab3b003873afac91771303883e","tid":2174272,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T20:04:50.000Z","msg":"　　多國傳媒在晚上報導，巴塞隆拿翼鋒美斯 (Lionel Messi) 已經向球會申請離隊，引起球迷熱話。<br />\n<br />\n　　巴塞隆拿前隊長、葡萄牙名將費高 (Luis Figo) 雖已年近五十，但在社交網站上的反應亦不比年輕人輸蝕。費高晚上在 Twitter 轉載了美斯申請離隊的新聞，並留下「嘩！！又一個歷史時刻！！！」的字句。<br />\n<br />\n　　費高上世紀九十年代於巴塞隆拿成名，二零零零年以破當時世界轉會費紀錄的一百億比塞塔（折合六千零十萬歐元）轉投死敵皇家馬德里。事隔二十年，費高仍然被老一輩巴塞隆拿球迷視為頭號叛徒，這次「慶祝」美斯轉會，會否又引來年輕一輩球迷的憎恨？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hrKgFsA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhrKgFsA.jpg&h=b73136c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44f57b2e13f946a3bf6f1721c47e5b362550a6a4","tid":2174272,"uid":165817,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T20:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.fcbarcelonanoticias.com/uploads/s1/20/29/06/cochinillo-202906.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fcbarcelonanoticias.com%2Fuploads%2Fs1%2F20%2F29%2F06%2Fcochinillo-202906.png&h=bde00ea0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9aa8904d55333b7ba2704d8e15af943f77ffe329","tid":2174272,"uid":201601,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T20:09:46.000Z","msg":"豬頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47a5ccccc98774468c0e7aa3caf22895d4f700b","tid":2174272,"uid":165817,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"9aa8904d55333b7ba2704d8e15af943f77ffe329","tid":2174272,"uid":201601,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T20:09:46.000Z","msg":"豬頭<img src=\